## Hardware Notes

This directory is reserved for hardware-specific documentation and future design files related to ApexPyro.

## Licensing Direction

Any future custom PCB designs, schematics, fabrication outputs, or related hardware source files added to this directory are intended to be licensed under the [CERN Open Hardware License Version 2 - Weakly Reciprocal](LICENSE-HARDWARE).

## Current Status

- No custom PCB design files are published here yet.
- The current controller build is documented primarily through wiring and integration notes in the main repository docs.

## Planned Contents

- Custom PCB design source files
- Schematics and board-level integration notes
- Manufacturing and assembly guidance when hardware designs are published
